    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.8.4">
<l>ciṟaiyā ruvaṇap puḷḷoṉṟē ṟiyaṉṟu ticaināṉ kunāṉku miriya ceruvil</l>
<l>kaṟaiyār neṭuvē larakkar maṭiyak kaṭalcū ḻilaṅkai kaṭantā ṉiṭantāṉ</l>
<l>muṟaiyāl vaḷarkkiṉ ṟamuttī yarnālvē taraivēḷ viyāṟaṅ karēḻi ṉicaiyōr</l>
<l>maṟaiyōr vaṇaṅkap pukaḻey tunāṅkūr maṇimā ṭa<supplied>k</supplied>kōyil vaṇaṅkeṉ maṉaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My heart, worship at Maṇimāṭa Temple in Nānkūr which gains praise</l>
<l rend="indent">since those of the three fires which [they] nurture as required,</l>
<l>Those of the four Vedas, those of the five sacrifices</l>
<l rend="indent">and six branches [of knowledge], those of the seven modes of music,</l>
<l rend="indent">and Vedic experts worship[there],</l>
<l>The very place of him who overcame sea-encircled Lanka,</l>
<l rend="indent">mounting a white-headed kite full of feathers,</l>
<l>So that the demons with long, bloody spears died that day in battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">when they were driven to the four-and-four directions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
